text: Omosarotes paradoxum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Tippmann in 1955. It is known from Panama, Ecuador, and Peru.BioLib.cz - Omosarotes paradoxum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Cyrtinini Category:Beetles described in 1955
